'''赫卢赫卢韦–印姆弗鲁兹公园'''（{{lang-en|'''Hluhluwe–Imfolozi Park'''}}），前身为'''赫卢赫卢韦–乌姆福洛济禁猎区'''，是非洲最古老的[[自然保护区|自然保护区]]。它包括960平方公里（96000公顷）的丘陵地形，位于[[南非|南非]][[夸祖魯-納塔爾省|夸祖魯-納塔爾省]][[德班|德班]]的中[[祖鲁王国|祖鲁兰]]向北{{convert|280|km}}，有丰富的野生动物和保护工作。<ref name = places>{{cite web|url = http://www.places.co.za/html/1979.html|title = Hluhluwe–Imfolozi Park|accessdate = 2008-06-07|publisher = SA Places|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180717070653/https://www.places.co.za/html/1979.html|archive-date = 2018-07-17|dead-url = yes}}</ref> 该公园是[[夸祖魯-納塔爾省|夸祖魯-納塔爾省]]唯一的国立公园，所有的[[非洲五霸|非洲五霸]]都会出现在这里。<ref name = places /> 保护区内有世界上数量最多的[[白犀|白犀]]。<ref name=game>{{cite web |url=http://www.game-reserve.com/south-africa_hluhluwe-umfolozi.html |title=Hluhluwe Umfolozi National Park |publisher=Game-Reserve.com |accessdate=2008-06-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117020048/http://www.game-reserve.com/south-africa_hluhluwe-umfolozi.html |archivedate=2015-11-17 }}</ref> 然而，然而，犀牛和公园的原生环境保护区现在正在受到一个建设露天煤矿的计划的威胁，日益壮大的环保人士联盟正争取停止这个计划。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://saveourwilderness.wordpress.com/2014/05/19/mining-threat-to-wilderness-reserve/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-11-17 |archive-date=2014-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140604121107/http://saveourwilderness.wordpress.com/2014/05/19/mining-threat-to-wilderness-reserve/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==历史==
[[Image:Spear_rock.jpg|thumb]]
在整个园区内有许多石器时代聚落留下的迹象，<ref name = accommodation/> 这片区域原本是祖鲁王国的皇家猎场，<ref name = where>{{cite web|url = http://www.wheretostay.co.za/information/topic/596|publisher = Where to stay|title = Hluhluwe Umfolozi Game Reserve|accessdate = 2008-06-07|archive-date = 2014-07-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140726002126/http://www.wheretostay.co.za/information/topic/596|dead-url = no}}</ref> 却在1895年建成公园。<ref name = places /> 乌姆福洛济和赫卢赫卢韦保护区主要保护白犀牛，白犀牛在当时就列在濒危物种名单上。<ref name = accommodation/> 该地区一直是携带{{le|那加那病|nagana}}的[[舌蠅屬|采采蝇]]的避风港，这种舌蝇在殖民时代阻止猎人破坏保护区。<ref name = accommodation/> 但是随着欧洲农民在祖鲁兰地区定居，人们指责这里的野生动物因为采采蝇而患病，并将这里变成了消灭苍蝇的试验区。<ref name = accommodation/> 1945年欧洲农民通过喷洒[[滴滴涕|滴滴涕]]杀害了约10万只动物解决这个问题。<ref name = accommodation/> 但自那以后，就很难再发现白犀牛的踪迹，现在也仅保存着1000头左右数目的种群。<ref name = accommodation/> 1995年4月30日，时任[[纳尔逊·曼德拉|纳尔逊·曼德拉]]总统参观了赫卢赫卢韦禁猎区以庆祝公园百年。赫卢赫卢韦–印姆弗鲁兹公园三个单独的保护区，1989年合并后使用现在的名称。<ref name = accommodation/>

==地理和气候==
[[Image:Black_Umfolozi_water.jpg|thumb]]导游在黑乌姆福洛济河畔挖水]]
该公园位于[[南非|南非]]东海岸的[[夸祖魯-納塔爾省|夸祖魯-納塔爾省]]。公园与[[姆圖巴圖巴|姆圖巴圖巴]]和[[赫盧赫盧韋|赫盧赫盧韋]]镇很近。该地区北部（赫卢赫卢韦区域）和南部（乌姆福洛济区域）的地理环境不同，赫卢赫卢韦–印姆弗鲁兹公园部分处于低疟区。<ref name=malaria_prevalence>{{cite web|url = http://www.santhnet.co.za/index.php/malaria-advice-for-travellers/item/330-malaria-risk-map-for-south-africa-2013.html|publisher = The South African National Travel Health Network (SaNTHNet)|title = Malaria risk map for South Africa|accessdate = 2014-10-20|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140306175912/http://www.santhnet.co.za/index.php/malaria-advice-for-travellers/item/330-malaria-risk-map-for-south-africa-2013.html|archivedate = 2014-03-06}}</ref>

===乌姆福洛济===
该区域位于两条{{le|乌姆福洛济河|Umfolozi River}}中间，北面是黑乌姆福洛济河（'Black Umfolozi'）和南面白乌姆福洛济河（'White Umfolozi'）。<ref name=accommodation>{{cite web|url = http://hluhluwe-accommodation.co.za/content/view/16/58/|publisher = Hluhluwe Accommodation|title = Hluhluwe–Umfolozi Game Reserve|accessdate = 2008-06-07|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080515162512/http://hluhluwe-accommodation.co.za/content/view/16/58/|archivedate = 2008-05-15}}</ref> 这片区域是公园的南部，一般夏季炎热、冬季轻度降温、但也有寒冷天气。<ref name = places/>

===赫卢赫卢韦===
乌姆福洛济地势范围从乌姆福洛济河河床的低地到陡峭的丘陵地带，其中包括一些宽而深的山谷。这一地区的栖息地主要是草原，延伸到金合欢热带稀树草原和林地。赫卢赫卢韦地区有丘陵地貌，海拔范围从{{convert|80|to|540|m}}。山脊沿着森林陡坡伸向森林山谷灌木的地势较低水平灌溉区域。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sabirding.co.za/birdspot/040540.asp |publisher=Southern African Birding cc |title=Hluhluwe-Umfolozi Park |year=2001 |last=Cowgill |first=Roy |last2=Davis |first2=Steve |last3=Forsythe |first3=Erik |accessdate=2008-06-07 |archive-date=2013-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130524013500/http://www.sabirding.co.za/birdspot/040540.asp |deadurl=yes }}</ref> 公园的北部是崎岖不平的山地森林和草原，被称为赫卢赫卢韦区域。<ref name = game />

